text: Daniel Allerstorfer (born 4 December 1992) is an Austrian judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's +100 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the first round by Renat Saidov. ==External links== * *UJZ Mühlviertel ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Austria Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:People from Rohrbach District Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games Category:European Games competitors for Austria Category:Judoka at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games medalists in judo Category:European Games bronze medalists for Austria Category:Sportspeople from Upper Austria
